<h2>Chapter 3: Segment Your Members by Lifecycle Stage</h2>
<p>Sending the same email to every contact on your list is the fastest way to increase unsubscribes. The fitness industry already has the highest unsubscribe rate of any sector at 0.40%. Segmentation fixes that.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="Gym member lifecycle email sequence map" src="/images/blog/gym-member-lifecycle-email-map.webp" /></p>
